cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically 3D object detection using monocular vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves autonomous navigation and driving, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves machine learning techniques, such as keypoint estimation and regression, which are commonly used in deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the accuracy and convergence of the proposed method, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing, specifically the use of region proposals, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL).
